      {
        "Language": "POL",
        "Name": "Ratunek przed mro\u017Anym losem!",
        "Client": "Zmarzni\u0119ta panna",
        "Description": "O, nie! Arktyczne potwory\r\nzbli\u017Caj\u0105 si\u0119 do ludzkich osad!\r\nNied\u0142ugo b\u0119dziemy pokryci\r\nlodem i nie b\u0119dzie mo\u017Cna spa\u0107!\r\nA\u017C mnie dreszcze z\u0142apa\u0142y!\r\nMusisz je zatrzyma\u0107.",
        "Target": "Upoluj wszystkie cele",
        "Fail": "Nagroda r\u00F3wna 0 lub\r\nkoniec czasu"
      },
      {
        "Language": "POR",
        "Name": "Liberdade do Frio Futuro!",
        "Client": "Menina Sens\u00EDvel ao Frio",
        "Description": "Ah, n\u00E3o, os monstros \u00E1rticos\r\nest\u00E3o chegando nos habitats\r\nhumanos! Desse jeito, vamos\r\nficar cobertos de gelo sem\r\npoder dormir \u00E0 noite! S\u00F3 de\r\npensar, me d\u00E1 arrepio! Voc\u00EA\r\ntem que det\u00EA-los!",
        "Target": "Cace todos os monstros-alvo",
        "Fail": "A recompensa chega a 0\r\nou o tempo expira"
      },
      {
        "Language": "KOR",
        "Name": "\uCD94\uC704 \uC18D\uC5D0\uC11C \uC7A0\uB4E4\uAE34 \uC2EB\uC5B4!",
